  <h1>中华人民共和国固体废物污染环境防治法（英）</h1>
  <h2>Law of the People's Republic of China</h2>
  <h3>on Prevention of Environmental Pollution  Caused by Solid Waste</h3>
  <p>
    Adopted by the 16th Meeting of the Standing  Committee of the Eighth National People's Congress on October 30, 1995,  promulgated by Order No.58of the President of the People's Republic of China  on October 30, 1995, to be effective as of April 1, 1996.</p>
 <span class="mulu">Contents</span>
